  2) Obesety rates https://data.wprdc.org/dataset/allegheny-county-obesity-rates/resource/fce248f0-8697-4d2a-bbe0-2da826776bfa
  3) Median Lifespan https://data.wprdc.org/dataset/median-age-death/resource/c2e1500a-a12a-4e91-be94-76c6a892b7e2

This project is our subjective view on which Pittsburgh neighborhood is the best based off "Health & Safety". We determined that based off 3 metrics (datasets above)
